    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in poor condition and is being sold strictly as-is. It has significant mechanical issues that will require professional attention before it can be considered roadworthy, along with high mileage and noticeable engine wear. The exterior shows substantial rust, various dents, and faded paint, while the interior has heavy staining and tears in the upholstery. This would be an ideal project car for a mechanic or a donor vehicle for parts.",
      "price": 4500.0,
