    },
    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Looking for a reliable and well-loved ride? This vehicle is in great shape and ready for its next adventure! It has been consistently maintained and drives beautifully, showing only minor signs of regular use. It's a solid, dependable choice for anyone wanting quality and value in one package!",
      "price": 34500.0,
